text: Ghanashyam Daha (Nepali: घनश्याम दाहाल) is Nepalese politician and member of the Bagmati Provincial Assembly and he was elected from Chitwan 2 (A) for the CPN (Maoist Centre). He had previously serving as Minister for Labour, Employment and Transport of Bagmati Province in Rajendra Pandey cabinet. == References == Category:Nepalese politicians Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Ghanashyam Dahal
